This tool will return an object that contains fields for the creation of a pie chart. 
The object contains the following fields: `values`, `labels`, and `caption`. 
The values field is an array of numbers representing the sizes of the pie chart segments. 
The labels field is an array of strings corresponding to each value, representing the categories or segments in the chart. 
The caption field is a string that provides a brief description or title for the pie chart.
Each value in the values array corresponds to the label at the same index in the labels array. The sum of all values represents the whole pie.

